Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,久能先生  是个没见过的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,别管他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:02.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是个小鬼是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是弄错地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:11.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:17.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫红真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:20.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我找少当家久能正先生有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:25.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,花村幼儿园的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什么设计啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:14.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,少当家久能正先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫红真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,红真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我们原来见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:21.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  去查一下红真九郎这人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没听说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:33.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那种小鬼 把他干掉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道花村幼儿园的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:39.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我来是因为有人骚扰花村幼儿园的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:39.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,骚扰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:40.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,上周园长的家被人潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,土地的权利证书被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,留下了园长孙子的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这是无言的恐吓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟警察商量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就会伤害到孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这与我们事务所有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系？这是你指使的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,花村幼儿园什么的听都没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:16.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你准备把花村幼儿园以及旁边的土地买下然后转让是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:21.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有久能先生指使购买花村幼儿园土地的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:25.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,还有部下回复的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:31.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这些是每天打到园长家里的无声电话的号码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这能作为民事案件解决吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,红君  你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,纠纷调解人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,纠纷调解人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:47.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那你希望什么交易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,请把土地的权利证书还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:55.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,还有请保证今后不对花村幼儿园出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我能得到什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我们销毁掌握的所有情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:01.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就这些就想让我收手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:07.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你要怎么让我相信你销毁了掌握的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那只能靠你相信我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真敢说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:13.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,又没其他办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,久能先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:15.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:18.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙认识的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是一个人来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哎  谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来找真九郎的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:27.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:32.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  你说过要保护紫的却跑到这种地方来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,还带着小孩来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:35.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你在我睡着的时候总是做这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了不能到外面来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:44.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小子  没法谈了  今天你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什么  那交易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我把证据散播出去你也不在乎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样麻烦的是久能先生你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:57.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  你们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:58.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,别多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:04.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,久能先生  我掌握的情报一定会全部销毁的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:09.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:20.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你之后绝对不再对花村幼儿园出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  送客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  紫  回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  这家伙很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫  别说这么失礼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  纠纷调解人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:46.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都写在你脸上了  骗子就是一副骗子的嘴脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:46.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  久能先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  别相信这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,纠纷调解人  赶紧走  到我忍耐的极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:07:00.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是  这就走  这家伙人有点怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.58,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当傻瓜  有哪点奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不要点头哈腰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:08.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不要生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:15.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎竟然相信那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:32.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:37.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  放开他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:42.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:43.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:48.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:51.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不要  放手  放…手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,骨头…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:57.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是  崩月的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:01.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是件重大的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:25.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是要与九凤院家为敌的相当重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:25.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不知道这孩子有多么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,给他好好说明就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:33.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然把她留在公寓然后自己跑到黑帮事务所去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:36.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太不小心了  你把这工作当什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:38.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,粗心大意  想法也太天真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都轻易下结论才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,弥生  冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:49.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  这不是你这种程度的男人能接手的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:58.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事也是会有的  今后你会注意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:09:59.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:02.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们今天就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:04.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:09.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,红香大人  我实在是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有交给你来做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为交给男人来做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:15.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:22.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,除我之外  明明还能找到很多能够保护她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么偏偏选红真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:27.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都说过是我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是怀疑红香大人的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:34.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  通过今天的事  红香大人应该也很明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这工作对红真九郎来说太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:42.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,他实力不足这点我很清楚  十分清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:43.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,现在先饶了我吧  以后会给你好好说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我要继续留在这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:54.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体不疼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:27.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了  早饭由紫来做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,继续睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫  昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:39.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没有好好听话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,让真九郎挨揍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:44.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没有生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,错的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是紫的任意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你生我的气也是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:54.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没有生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,错的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:57.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸上有写着骗人两字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:03.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你平安无事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的早饭就交给紫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎好好休息就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这个还能吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  睡眠不足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看了晚间直播吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:22.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那个真好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,后藤MM感觉不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  后藤MM啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是防守方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:37.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小紫  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:38.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这房间什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,臭的不是被子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:53.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  一般进房间的时候总该敲个门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这可是新闻部的部室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,新闻部的部员只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:00.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  这是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,把其他部员赶出去的是谁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你是来报告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,顺利解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可以对园长说没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大概可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大概  真不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我总之是去解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:19.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不知他们是否就此收手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,总之先看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:26.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只是摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,和他们起争执了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:38.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这圆珠笔真便利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:39.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,上次也被外国人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是俄罗斯人吧  问路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:43.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你大意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是涉及小紫的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:56.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:57.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这是其他工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:00.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:04.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,作为崩月家的人  忠告一句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:09.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要用到角的工作别接比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我拿伤药来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:16.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有爷爷做的为不成熟的弟子所准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:17.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:24.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有气味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:30.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么把被子摆在我房间门口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在晒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这里采光点最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎的被子臭得受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去对身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,确实  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才在帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:49.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不成熟  不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:50.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你确实不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我的被子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,为了少女的健康我才允许放在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  变得干净了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天环教我打扫房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎的被子也晒在走廊里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:26.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我住在这里  偶尔也该打扫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,还有肮脏的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要洗头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:53.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快看  真九郎  我终于成功独自洗头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,涂洗发精很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:01.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,渗进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:02.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:07.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  还疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因我的错  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是紫的错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:22.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我有许多旧伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕是处理纠纷事件的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,像勋章一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可以先出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:35.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:39.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和真九郎待同样时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,数到20就出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4  5  6  7  8
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:44.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天能看到星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明早会很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:53.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,呐  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:54.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:59.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎为什么要当纠纷调解人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:04.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为憧憬红香小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:09.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,红香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,红香是那么好的女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:19.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,比起紫  环  暗绘  夕乃还要好的女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:24.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是作为女人的角度  只是想变得像红香小姐那样强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我在和紫一样大的时候还很胆小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:29.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:31.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎小时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:35.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,很无聊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道许多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫也想变强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:39.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,强?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:40.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,想变强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,绑架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:51.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  把机场炸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:54.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,掳走存活下来的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,红在那之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,双亲在那时候去世的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:03.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,已经超过危险  害怕之类的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:04.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,非常疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐没有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:11.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,会有这种事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,脑中一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:18.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,死都不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:19.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:22.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:30.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  有什么好笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你  想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  死也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真嚣张  既然想死就成全你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明明想死的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候那个人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:07.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们这类专家才能完成的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就一会的工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:29.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧  将孩子带到外面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:31.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:32.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:34.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:37.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了  来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟随了红香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不久就寄宿在夕乃家里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,学了八年崩月流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然非常辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因此也拥有了如今的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:56.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,红香  让我成为了纠纷调解人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:03.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为真九郎的努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,现在才刚刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很像  那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只有真九郎才能理解紫的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:20.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此他的力量还…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那是很久之前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:34.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天能把小姐  紫带到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:35.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因为不知道怎么做才拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就算去外面了又怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:44.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里什么也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:48.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里就会有与我同样的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:49.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,莲丈大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:55.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经生下了三个小孩  已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,期待莲丈大人也没用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:02.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不想让紫拥有与我同样的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,莲丈大人也不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:08.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,莲丈大人可是爱着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人无法舍弃九凤院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:13.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:15.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我很感谢他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:22.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,比起迄今为止里之院的女人来说我是很自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:25.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  想让紫去见识外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:28.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要拥有比我更美好的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是困难的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能请你接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  她已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:43.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是紫的亲生母亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,九凤院苍树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,没能战胜家族规矩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:53.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在九凤院工作过我才知道  那家族很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:57.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,看着年幼的紫  我觉得必须接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:01.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这对真九郎来说太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:06.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  对他来说也是有好处的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,想保护谁的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:11.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,会让人变强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:14.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我如此坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:17.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我去大久保了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:20.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我走着去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:21.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是去五月雨庄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:22.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,情况我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:28.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  还是担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:30.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.30,0:24:21.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,下集  红
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:24.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,愿望
